{"tid":2156024,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得自己講嘢退步咗?","createTime":"2020-08-14T07:25:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T06:43:17.000Z","uid":363087,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"33ad4cdbc4520f79839b67b55db6ff6060ca8a7f","tid":2156024,"uid":363087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:25:42.000Z","msg":"自上年11月開始基本上唔使點返學， 然後sem2開學又淨係返咗一個禮拜<br />\n<br />\n加埋疫情 ，基本上冇乜點約啲friend出街， 日日喺屋企打機<br />\n<br />\n最近打機同friend講嘢嗰陣發覺自己講嘢退步咗， 可能打機講嚟講去都係某部分嘅用語<br />\n<br />\n到傾番啲正常嘢嗰陣講得冇咁流利了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"038b86acad8e7063b33c678185b802fcb171a325","tid":2156024,"uid":363087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:27:33.000Z","msg":"最近真係覺得自己講嘢冇咁流利， 可能會卡一卡先諗到個詞係乜/ 或者有時會講錯咗啲名詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75cfb3fe1edb8f9e97c9b3c7d7fc83c77e32f908","tid":2156024,"uid":3852,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:39:41.000Z","msg":"你就好<br />\n我啞撚埋"},{"pid":"766f578445bbc871668d46321957d4291a089f9b","tid":2156024,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75cfb3fe1edb8f9e97c9b3c7d7fc83c77e32f908","tid":2156024,"uid":3852,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:39:41.000Z","msg":"你就好<br />\n我啞撚埋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:44:44.000Z","msg":"我聲帶退化到冇咗"},{"pid":"1dea124be85fbca68d7e51a1ed15a7dddf8866d3","tid":2156024,"uid":180124,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:46:22.000Z","msg":"會<br />\n太耐冇社交個人會變得唔識開話題"},{"pid":"eb75926f3f7d49221cc0a428f383080b9af3236b","tid":2156024,"uid":76747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:46:23.000Z","msg":"是但啦<br />\n唔返返學係屋企有機比你打仲想點"},{"pid":"aa9e033913362a5f1fb2a10faa43beb04718cdce","tid":2156024,"uid":185238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T07:53:48.000Z","msg":"刷亠聙札机㽊都仈鴧寥尸"},{"pi